---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="NIE Conference 2022" description="NIE Conference and PhD Symposium 2022">
  <section class="container page-content">
    <header class="section-header">
      <h1 class="gradient-text">NIE Conference & PhD Symposium 2022</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="image-wrapper main-image">
      <img src="/images/NIE2022/group1.jpg" alt="NIE 2022" class="responsive-image rounded-image shadow" />
    </div>

    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <p>The School of Business and Economics (SBE) at Loughborough University hosted a two-day event: the PhD Symposium in Industrial Economics and the Network of Industrial Economists (NIE) conference on July 7 and 8, 2022.</p>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider" />

    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <h2>PhD Symposium</h2>
      <p class="date"><strong>July 7th, 2022</strong></p>
      <p>The Symposium brought together early career economists (PhD students, Postdocs, etc.) to foster discussion and dissemination of research in all areas of industrial economics. A number of external academics acted as discussants and provided high-quality feedback.</p>

      <h2>NIE Conference</h2>
      <p class="date"><strong>July 8th, 2022</strong></p>
      <p>The NIE conference consisted of presentations by five prominent industrial economists.</p>
      <ul class="styled-list">
        <li><a href="https://sites.google.com/site/allainml/home" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Marie-Laure Allain</a> (CNRS and CREST, Ecole Polytechnique)</li>
        <li><a href="http://chloelecoq.org" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chloé Le Coq</a> (University of Paris II Panthéon-Assas, CRED)</li>
        <li><a href="https://toomas.hinnosaar.net" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Toomas Hinnosaar</a> (University of Nottingham)</li>
        <li><a href="https://www.southampton.ac.uk/people/5x25wc/professor-carmine-ornaghi" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Carmine Ornaghi</a> (University of Southampton)</li>
        <li><a href="https://www.wbs.ac.uk/about/person/john-thanassoulis/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">John Thanassoulis</a> (Warwick Business School)</li>
      </ul>
      <p><a href="/files/NIE-BooksofAbstracts-2022.pdf" class="btn btn-secondary">Conference Agenda & Book of Abstracts</a></p>
    </div>

    <hr class="divider" />

    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <h2>Some memories from the conference</h2>
      <div class="gallery">
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <img src="/images/NIE2022/presenter2.jpg" alt="NIE 2022 Presenter" class="responsive-image rounded-image shadow" />
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <img src="/images/NIE2022/presenter1.jpg" alt="Ana" class="responsive-image rounded-image shadow" />
        </div>
        <div class="gallery-item">
          <img src="/images/NIE2022/theatre1.jpg" alt="Theatre" class="responsive-image rounded-image shadow" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .page-content {
    padding: 4rem 1rem;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-top: 3rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .date {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .content-wrapper {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.8;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  .content-wrapper p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content-wrapper a {
    color: var(--accent-primary);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .content-wrapper a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-secondary);
  }

  .divider {
    border: none;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--divider);
    margin: 3rem 0;
  }

  .image-wrapper.main-image {
    margin: 2rem 0 3rem;
  }

  .responsive-image {
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .rounded-image {
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-lg);
  }

  .shadow {
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
  }

  .styled-list {
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .styled-list li {
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 0.8rem 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1rem;
    border-radius: var(--border-radius-sm);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: var(--font-base);
    text-decoration: none !important;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--accent-primary) !important;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-primary);
  }

  .btn-secondary:hover {
    background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.1);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .gallery {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }
  
  .gallery-item img {
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }
</style>
